mathematica: max = 18; s[x_] := 1+Sum[ (2*n-1)!!*x^n, {n, 1, max+1}]; g[x_] := 1+Sum[b[n]*x^n, {n, 1, max+1}]; bb = Series[ 1-1/s[x]-x*g[x]*s[x], {x, 0, max+1}] // CoefficientList[#, x]&; solb = Thread[bb == 0] // Solve // First; a[0] = 1; aa = Series[ g[x]-(1+g[x]*Sum[ a[n]*(x*g[x]^2*s[x]^2)^n, {n, 1, max+1}]), {x, 0, max+1}] /. solb // CoefficientList[#, x]&; sola = Thread[aa == 0] // Most // Solve // First; Table[a[n], {n, 0, max}] /. sola (* _Jean-Fran√ßois Alcover_, Aug 14 2013 *)
